summary: so i watched detective pikachu yesterday and it was great but three things were greatest: 1) pokemons were used instead of...
body:
so i watched detective pikachu yesterday and it was great but three things were greatest:

1) pokemons were used instead of speakers (beatbox scene on youtube, just watch it okay, it’s SO FUCKING CREATIVE)

2) the boy and the girl didn’t kiss after having zero chemistry, thank god

3) the twists were 100% plausible, after they happened you immediately knew which parts were foreshadowing them

+ bonus: happy ending!!!
